%% ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
%%  Telnet-SML — COMPLETE SYSTEM ARCHITECTURE DIAGRAM (Mermaid)
%%  Physical Relay Device → C++ Backend → Transport → Browser UI
